statements.sql: select `page_tbls`.*, `permissions`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `permissions`.`page_id` as `pivot_page_id` from `page_tbls` inner join `permissions` on `page_tbls`.`id` = `permissions`.`page_id` where `permissions`.`user_id` in (1)

select `students_tbls`.`id` as `student_id`, `sections_tbls`.`id` as `section_id`, `enrollment_tbls`.*, CONCAT(students_tbls.last_name, ', ',students_tbls.first_name, ' ',students_tbls.middle_name) as student_name from `students_tbls` inner join `enrollment_tbls` on `enrollment_tbls`.`student_id` = `students_tbls`.`id` inner join `sections_tbls` on `enrollment_tbls`.`section_id` = `sections_tbls`.`id` where `section_id` = '3'
